pyfitsh
======

pyfitsh is a Python/Cython interface and compatibility reimplementation based on
FITSH.

Upstream FITSH:
  Website: https://www.fitsh.net/
  Author: András Pál
  License: GNU General Public License, version 3 or later (GPL-3.0-or-later)

Portions of this repository are derived from, adapted from, or interface with
the FITSH source code.

Original FITSH copyright notices are preserved in the corresponding source
files where applicable. Modifications for pyfitsh are copyright the pyfitsh
contributors.

